{
  "stem": "4189.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And to count these people takes a long time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And you had to stand at attention in rain or shine, in winter or summer.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "You had to stand still in rows of tens with a space in between, just like soldiers, and had to be counted.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "The dead people had to be lined up on the side so that the count had to be complete.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And if one was missing, you had to stay there for hours until they found out if somebody escaped or if somebody was hiding, till they found them.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So the conditions were really impossible.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So since there was so much building going on there, I found out that they had a [NON-ENGLISH], a school where they were teaching young people how to lay bricks, because they needed a lot of brick layers because of all this construction.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they were taking young people and sending them to the school to learn how to lay bricks.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And right away I applied for that job because then you were inside the school.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We got the same food as the other people got, but we were protected from the elements.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I applied for the school, and I went to this so-called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they taught us how to lay bricks, how to mix certain mortars, and how to lay-- make walls and chimneys.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Different type of construction.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This went on for about two months.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "After two months, it was a big help to us, because the ones that were in the school, like I said, were much better off than the people that had to go to work and were outside.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So after two months they said, OK, now, now you know how to lay bricks, now you go to work.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
